Title: Wicked Game (2)
Plot: A shocking and brutal conclusion awaits Allison and Cynthia as they delve into the decade-old case of the kidnapping and murder of Cynthia's daughter. Meanwhile, Joe tries to get funding for a new invention and Bridgette predicts good fortunes for her dad.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and horror scenes. Content may disturb
GuestStars: Sarah Drew, Susan Goodwillie, Lily Rabe, Steven Flynn
